node.text: I can’t believe we’re heading into the last two weeks of the  @weglow 66 day challenge 🤩 I’ve loved being on this journey with you all and watching you glow. You should be so proud 🧡 As usual, this evening I want to bring you more light & motivation as we head into the next week, now I feel we need it more than ever✨ Today’s story is from @hannahcleeve - who is such a pure soul & the way this superstar moves is just out of this world, I’m in total awe of her 🙏🏻 Hannah’s words resonate with me so much & I hope you can all take something from them too. Please take a moment to listen or read what she has to say & tag someone that needs to hear this 🥰 @hannahcleeve

node.text:
Happy Valentine’s Day everyone; I hope today’s “Stories that Glow” reminds you to work on loving yourself today - as the most important relationship you’ll ever have is the one you have with yourself ❤️

This weeks story is about the  incredibly talented Sophie @sophcaz ⚡️ and her journey to find what truly helps her to glow from the inside out. I was so excited to meet Sophie, a GB athlete (brings back sporting memories & team moral) 🙌🏼 Sophie is so down to Earth, chatty and just exudes confidence in her own skin and who she is ✨ So if you can spare a few minutes to watch & listen between scrolling I guarantee you’ll come away glowing 🧡
